2003-07-14  ryanbaldwin
	* src/native/jaygds/source/entrypoints.cpp:
		Introduced a hack into nativeInitilize to allow this method to be called multiple
		times with different client library names until one is sucsefully loaded.

	* src/native/jaygds/source/allocator.cpp:
		Fix for solaris sparc and other platforms where aligment is important.
		
		ScratchPadAllocator now allocates all memory on eight byte boundary.
		Hopefully this will be OK for all platforms.

	* src/main/org/firebirdsql/ngds/GDS_Impl.java:
		Modified the way nativeInitilize is called to clean up code
		make it easier to modify list of client librarys tried.

	* build_native.xml:
		Fixed build on unix platforms.

2003-07-13  ryanbaldwin
	* src/main/org/firebirdsql/ngds/GDS_Impl.java:
	* src/main/org/firebirdsql/ngds/GDS_Impl.java:
		Dont specify .dll extension when loading firebird client
		library.

	* build.xml:
		Fix unix builds.

	* src/native/jaygds/source/generic_unix/platform.cpp:
	* src/native/jaygds/source/generic_unix/platform.h:
		Should hopefully be the same on unix like platforms.

	* build_native.xml:
	* build_native.xml:
		Fix solaris build.

	* build.xml:
	* src/main/org/firebirdsql/ngds/GDS_Impl.java:
	* src/test/org/firebirdsql/ngds/TestNgds.java:
		Added target 'compile-native' to build.xml that builds the native library.
		This target invokes build_native.xml. For this to work either the JAVA_HOME
		environment variable needs to be set when invoking ant or the java_home ant
		property needs to be set too the root of the JDK.
		
		Added ngds package under src/test which contains a TesNgds test class which
		is essentially the same class as TestGds except it tests the ngds package.
		build.xml has been modified to make sure this test is not executed unless the
		'compile-native' target has been run sucsesfully.

