2002-02-02  d_jencks
	* src/stylesheets/details1.xsl:
	* src/stylesheets/junit-frames.xsl:
	* src/stylesheets/summary1.xsl:
	* src/stylesheets/summary1a.xsl:
	* src/stylesheets/summary2.xsl:
		xsl stylsheets for junitreport

	* src/lib/log4j-core.jar:
		log4j-core.jar from log4j version 1.0.4. Log4j is used for all
		logging, however the jar may be ommitted if you do not want
		logging.

	* lib/xalan.jar:
		xalan 2.2.0

	* src/resources/log4j.properties:
		Example log4j property file

	* lib/xml-apis.jar:
		xml-apis.jar from xalan 2.2.0 package

	* lib/xerces.jar:
		xerces 1.4.4 from xalan 2.2.0 package

	* lib/jaxp.jar:
	* lib/parser.jar:
		removed unused xml parsers

	* lib/ant.jar:
	* lib/optional.jar:
		ant version 1.4.1

2002-01-07  d_jencks
	* src/resources/META-INF/ra.xml:
	* src/resources/isc_error_msg.properties:
	* src/resources/ra.xml:
		Revised FBManager to create dialect 3 databases, and the tests
		to use a newly created database. Simplified and unified test
		constants. Test targets are now all-tests for all tests and one
		test for one test: specify the test as -Dtest=Gds one-test for
		the TestGds.class test.  Made a few other small changes to
		improve error messages

2002-01-05  d_jencks
	* src/lib/concurrent.jar:
		added Doug Lea's concurrent.jar, classes from Concurrent
		Programming in java, 2nd edition

2001-12-05  d_jencks
	* src/resources/ra.xml:
		Made connections use username and password from subject, added
		default user name and password properties to ManagedConnectionFactory

